rows.label: bf06280100_0010
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Ukh-!

rows.label: bf06280100_0020
rows.name: ...Move aside.

rows.label: bf06280100_0030
rows.name: Wild Roar!

rows.label: bf06280100_0040
rows.name: It's no use.

rows.label: bf06280100_0050
rows.name:
As expected, it seems the ether
energy is being blocked.

rows.label: bf06280100_0060
rows.name: Dammit!

rows.label: bf06280100_0070
rows.name: While we're doing this, Homura is...!

rows.label: bf06280100_0080
rows.name: We have to do something!

rows.label: bf06280100_0090
rows.name:
It's useless, Rex. You're
just wasting your energy.

rows.label: bf06280100_0100
rows.name:
The walls and floor seem to be quite
thick. We can't make any impact on them.

rows.label: bf06280100_0110
rows.name: Let's calm down a bit, Rex.

rows.label: bf06280100_0120
rows.name:
If we think calmly, we'll
come up with something!

rows.label: bf06280100_0130
rows.name: Hey, you there, help us out a little.

rows.label: bf06280100_0140
rows.name: Pointless struggling.

rows.label: bf06280100_0150
rows.name:
The way they built this place... It's
essentially one giant stasis web.

rows.label: bf06280100_0160
rows.name:
Stasis web... Like those
nets you used in Torigo?

rows.label: bf06280100_0170
rows.name:
To lock Drivers up together with their
Blades, and even leave us our weapons...

rows.label: bf06280100_0180
rows.name: They must have the utmost confidence.

rows.label: bf06280100_0190
rows.name:
Even if we manage to break
through given enough time

rows.label: bf06280100_0200
rows.name:
they probably plan to dispose
the Holy Grail before then.

rows.label: bf06280100_0210
rows.name: "Dispose"...

rows.label: bf06280100_0220
rows.name:
In that case, we need
your strength as well...

rows.label: bf06280100_0230
rows.name: I said it's pointless.

rows.label: bf06280100_0240
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Grr.

rows.label: bf06280100_0250
rows.name:
We won't get anywhere...
with brute force, that is.
